fields.title: Salomon Sight Snowboard
fields.description: Salomon Sight will get you from the ridgelines on top to the groomers below. The Cross Profile Camber is made for stability while charging and the rocker at the tip and tail add a bit of float in the deep.

fields.title: Roxy Gordon Snowboard - Woman's
fields.description:
The Roxy Gordon Snowboard is custom-made for riders progressing from zero to shred. 
Base color displayed may not be available. Base colors may vary.

fields.title: Anon Rodan Helmet
fields.description: Helmet has a clean, minimalist design that can get even simpler with removable ear pads and goggle retainer. The built-in passive ventilation makes sure your cranium stays cool.

fields.title: Outseam Gloves
fields.description: Engineered with articulated EVA padding along the back of hand and fingers for protection.

fields.title: Vans Standard Boots
fields.description: Meet the new standard of a modern winter boot. You get traction, warmth, and waterproofing in a package that's dripping with classic Vans style.

fields.title: Standard Mid Snow Boots
fields.description: A downsized version of the best-selling Standard snow boot, the Mid Boots have waterproof seam-sealed construction, a super durable Standard Snow outsole. and enough insulation to keep your toes toasty.

fields.title: Multi Pants
fields.description: Pants are a go-anywhere, do-anything pant for the dude who can't seem to sit still.

fields.title: Easy Rider Pants
fields.description: Pants aren't trying to reinvent the wheel. They're just darn good snow pants. They're durable, waterproof, breathable, and warm.

fields.title: Wave Snowboard
fields.description: The short, volume-shifted shape whips around obstacles with ease uplifted sidebases and narrow centerbase make edge-to-edge transitions even easier.

fields.title: Black Backpack
fields.description: With just enough room for your avy essentials, backup goggles, snacks and water.

fields.title: Blue Backpack
fields.description: Backpack lets you pack what you need without sacrificing speed and comfort.

fields.title: Men's Snowboard Jacket
fields.description: Jacket has fashion-forward flair, light insulation, and breathable-waterproof prowess that looks good and keeps you warm walking to the bar or sliding off the flat box.

fields.title: Woman's Burton Jacket
fields.description: With Jacket, you'll be warm and ready to go when the snow is extra slidey.

fields.title: Line 5-Finger Gloves
fields.description: Full-impregnated cowhide outers, foam + G-Loft insulation, a removable liner, and neoprene cuffs to seal the deal, the Fall Line 5-Finger Gloves are raising the bar on what to expect from ski/snowboard gloves.

fields.title: Blue Backpack
fields.description: Backpack lets you pack what you need without sacrificing speed and comfort.
